er contido nos livros, dá conselhos de vária ordem, desde o governo económico da casa, o trato com as criadas, até o convívio entre cônjuges, os ciúmes, etc.\nFundamentando-se na moral cristã, atribui à mulher função subalterna à do marido e um âmbito geográfico que terminaria nas quatro paredes da casa: a seu ver, a mulher deveria ser praticamente analfabeta e submissa para ser feliz.<\/span>\n  <a data-text-id=\"17872254693477174116\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"swapContent(\$(this));; return false;\">...more<\/a>\n\n    <\/div>\n\n      <div class=\'wtrButtonContainer wtrSignedOut\' id=\'12_book_4698221\'>\n<div class=\'wtrUp wtrLeft\'>\n<form action=\"/shelf/add_to_shelf\" accept-charset=\"UTF-8\" method=\"post\"><input name=\"utf8\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"&#x2713;\" /><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"authenticity_token\" value=\"o3NYY2uNuX6630gVcsrILAnL8kqQ+6r9tXJxCDoDynRNE7URkmMJ1GGwysgWFCjJByXXImKzlPO+nZZFoBFmIQ==\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"book_id\" id=\"book_id\" value=\"4698221\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"name\" id=\"name\" value=\"to-read\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"unique_id\" id=\"unique_id\" value=\"12_book_4698221\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"wtr_new\" id=\"wtr_new\" value=\"true\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"from_choice\" id=\"from_choice\" value=\"false\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"from_home_module\" id=\"from_home_module\" value=\"false\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"ref\" id=\"ref\" value=\"\" class=\"wtrLeftUpRef\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"existing_review\" id=\"existing_review\" value=\"false\" class=\"wtrExisting\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"book_origin\" id=\"book_origin\" value=\"related_works\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"page_url\" id=\"page_url\" value=\"/book/show/314582.The_Book_of_the_Courtier\" />\n<button class=\'wtrToRead\' type=\'submit\'>\n<span class=\'progressTrigger\'>Want to Read<\/span>\n<span class=\'progressIndicator\'>saving…<\/span>\n<\/button>\n<\/form>\n\n<\/